Populated Places & Historical Markers in Middlesex and Suffolk, MA @jahredwithanh

The interactive map below shows U.S. populated places and historical markers in two counties in Massachusetts (Middlesex and Suffolk). Data are from the National Map Staged Products Directory (US Board of Geographic Names) and the Historical Marker Database USA Index. County boundaries are also shown.

To change layers, click on the panel in the bottom right. Click a point to read historical information or access other links, if available.
